Earn when you buy stuff

Everywhere Mastercard® is accepted, you can pay with Fluz and get money back. We’re talking 1.5% minimum, and up to 25% at some stores. Limitless, catch-free, in your account in minutes. Boom.

Disclaimer

There are no fees for funding your digital wallet via ACH debit, or using the balance to transfer to other Fluz members, funding gift card purchases, funding a Mastercard transaction or withdrawing your balance to a bank account or PayPal account. You may incur fees from the bank or PayPal associated with your transaction to receive the funds from Fluz. Please consult your bank or PayPal account for further details. There are fees paid to Fluz to fund your digital wallet via debit card, credit card, prepaid card or PayPal.

The Fluz promise

We’re here to make your money work harder – plain and simple. That means we’ll protect and maximize it any way we can.

Trip-wire free

No need to switch banks, pass credit checks or worry about hidden fees. And we’ll never ask you to put money into Fluz to enjoy rewards.

✕
Disclaimer

1 Members can use Fluz app in conjunction with the bank accounts, debit or credit cards they already have. Members do not need to commit to annual or monthly membership fees.

2 There are no fees for 1-time card and gift card transactions funded by a US bank account made in the US. There are fees for funding your digital wallet balance via Debit or Credit card. There are international currency conversion fees charged by Visa for international transactions on the 1-time card.

No hidden fees
No credit checks
No small print

Top security

Can’t clone something that’s not there. Fluz creates a new 1-time card for every transaction. Nothing for you to lose, or for anyone else to use.

✕
Disclaimer

Fluz 1-time cards offer added security for members by adding a required process for FaceID, TouchID, 2-Factor Authentication or an account passcode on each transaction. The card number expires after 24-hours and after each use.
